'''沙勒姆·亞拉克姆撞擊坑'''（{{lang-en|Sholem Aleichem}}）是一個位於[[水星|水星]]的撞擊坑，中心座標51°N, 56.5°W，直徑190公里，以猶太裔俄羅斯意第緒語作家[[沙勒姆·亞拉克姆|沙勒姆·亞拉克姆]]命名<ref>[http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/5495 Sholem Aleichem.] {{Wayback|url=http://planetarynames.wr.usgs.gov/Feature/5495 |date=20170329232147 }} Gazetteer of Planetary Nomenclature</ref>。信使號拍攝影像中可見該撞擊坑底有沉積物存在，並且坑內構造已經被線型山脊改變<ref>[http://messenger.jhuapl.edu/gallery/sciencePhotos/image.php?gallery_id=2&image_id=122 MESSENGER: MErcury Surface, Space ENvironment, GEochemistry, and Ranging<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131115212738/http://messenger.jhuapl.edu/gallery/sciencePhotos/image.php?gallery_id=2&image_id=122 |date=2013-11-15 }}</ref>。

